ernight. It helps lock hydration into the skin, preventing dryness while keeping your complexion soft, refreshed, comfortable, and naturally glowing longer.<\/p>"}},"faq_eDQftN":{"type":"faq","settings":{"faq_title":"Does The Jelly Texture Feel Greasy?","faq_description":"<p>No, the lightweight jelly texture absorbs quickly into the skin without leaving a greasy or sticky feeling. It delivers deep hydration while feeling refreshing, breathable, and comfortable for everyday skincare use and layering.<\/p>"}},"faq_HbVdct":{"type":"faq","settings":{"faq_title":"Can I Apply It Before Makeup?","faq_description":"<p>Yes, the smooth fast-absorbing formula works beautifully under makeup. It helps prep the skin with hydration, creating a softer and smoother base that allows makeup to apply more evenly and naturally throughout the day.<\/p>"}},"faq_AATrbF":{"type":"faq","settings":{"faq_title":"Does It Help Improve Uneven Texture?","faq_description":"<p>Yes, the collagen-rich formula helps soften rough patches and improve overall skin texture with regular use. Skin appears smoother, healthier, and more refined while maintaining long-lasting hydration and a natural radiant-looking glow.<\/p>"}},"faq_6RDcBp":{"type":"faq","settings":{"faq_title":"Is This Product Good For Dry Skin?","faq_description":"<p>Definitely. ORELLA Collagen Jelly Cream deeply moisturizes dry and dehydrated skin while helping strengthen the moisture barrier. It leaves skin feeling soft, nourished, comfortable, and visibly healthier without heavy residue or irritation afterward.<\/p>"}},"faq_UYdF9V":{"type":"faq","settings":{"faq_title":"Can I Use It As Overnight Mask?","faq_description":"<p>Yes, applying a thicker layer before bedtime works as an intensive overnight moisture treatment. It helps replenish hydration while supporting smoother, softer, and more refreshed-looking skin by the next morning naturally.<\/p>"}},"faq_nmFjac":{"type":"faq","settings":{"faq_title":"What Makes Hydrolyzed Collagen Beneficial?","faq_description":"<p>Hydrolyzed collagen is broken into smaller particles for easier skin absorption. It helps support hydration, elasticity, and smoother-looking skin while improving softness and promoting a firmer, healthier-looking complexion with continued regular use.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["faq_JjfJjR","faq_eDQftN","faq_HbVdct","faq_AATrbF","faq_6RDcBp","faq_UYdF9V","faq_nmFjac"],"name":"Faqs Accordion","settings":{"animation":"","setwidth":"container","background_section":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","e_size":"cover","e_repeat":"no-repeat","e_pos":"center center","subtitle_top":"FAQ","replace_reviews":false,"reviews_type":"t_1","title":"Frequently Asked Questions","description":"","align_heading":"center","title_size":"h6","subtitle_top_color":"","heading_color":"","description_color":"","e_first_open":false,"e_reverse":true,"e_small":true,"faq_content":"","e_right":false,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":80,"mobile_padding_top":20,"mobile_padding_bottom":20}},"text_images_slider_hH6brh":{"type":"text_images_slider","blocks":{"text_block_hKLU8E":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"width":"100%","bgtext":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","title_color":"#fff2f4","subtitle":"Community Glow","replace_reviews":true,"reviews_type":"t_1","title":"Real Results Daily","size_text":"h2","text":"","answer_content":"<p>From daily skincare routines to glowing self-care moments, our growing community shares authentic results, radiant transformations, and renewed confidence through collagen-powered hydration and nourishment every single day.<\/p><p><\/p>","style_btn":"btn-theme","button":"GET YOURS","link":"#","block_align":"center","align":"left"}},"video_jnjhBE":{"type":"video","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/REV8.jpg","video_pick":""}},"video_jryd6M":{"type":"video","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/REV5.jpg","video_pick":""}},"video_7q7rGW":{"type":"video","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/REV1_f91644c9-b460-48a4-a523-82c0b9e2b386.jpg","video_pick":""}},"v